1. Prepare package directory

packages/com.shoderitz.AccessCvs/
    data/
        <place all files to be installed here>
        AccessCvs.dll
        Qt5Core.dll
        ...

    meta/
        package.xml
        installscript.qs
        ...


2. Build installer

Build this project.


3. Make repository with repogen.exe

cd AccessCvsInstaller
/ifw-install-dir/repogen.exe -p packages/ repository/


4. Upload repository

Upload all files under repository/ to web server.
